            <title>ChatGPT 崩了，OpenAI 回应称正在调查</title>
            <description>&lt;div class=&quot;tougao-user&quot;&gt;感谢 IT 之家网友 &lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D810309&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;重拾韶华&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1828940&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Liu_&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D2156801&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;石岛&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1654490&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;清欢岁&lt;/a&gt; 的线索投递！&lt;/div&gt;
